headline: The J.M. Smucker Co. Announces Plans to Close Indianapolis Manufacturing Facility in Continued Optimization of Sweet Baked Snacks Segment
summary: The J.M. Smucker Co. (NYSE: SJM) announced today plans to close its Indianapolis, Indiana manufacturing facility, which manufactures products from the Company's Hostess® brand, and consolidate operations into other existing facilities. The Company will close and pursue the sale of its Indianapolis manufacturing facility by early calendar year 2026.
